#. translators: JS template tokens (not sprintf): {m} = module side count, {b} = encoded byte length, {e} = effective EC level (L/M/Q/H).
#: src/Admin/Menu.php:151 src/Block/Maker.php:162
msgid "{m}×{m} modules · {b} bytes · EC {e}"
msgstr "{m}×{m} modules · {b} octets · EC {e}"

#. translators: JS template tokens: {lw}×{lh} = logo size in QR modules, {lp} = actual coverage % of QR area. Leading separator part of the format.
#: src/Admin/Menu.php:153 src/Block/Maker.php:164
msgid " · Logo {lw}×{lh} ({lp}%)"
msgstr " · Logo {lw}×{lh} ({lp} %)"

#: src/Admin/Menu.php:154 src/Block/Maker.php:165
msgid ""
"Past ~512 bytes the QR gets dense — print it large (≥ 4 cm) for reliable "
"scans, especially at high error correction."
msgstr ""
"Au-delà de ~512 octets le QR devient dense — imprimez-le grand (≥ 4 cm) pour "
"rester scannable, surtout en correction d’erreur élevée."

#: src/Admin/Menu.php:155 src/Block/Maker.php:166
msgid ""
"Past ~1024 bytes the QR may be unscannable on many phones — shorten the "
"content for reliable scans."
msgstr ""
"Au-delà de ~1024 octets le QR risque d’être illisible sur beaucoup de "
"smartphones — raccourcissez le contenu pour des scans fiables."

#: src/Admin/Menu.php:156
msgid ""
"Tick Tracking above — the QR will then encode a short /qr/… URL and the "
"contact card will be served as a downloadable .vcf file (works on every "
"scanner)."
msgstr ""
"Activez le suivi ci-dessus — le QR encodera alors une URL courte /qr/… et la "
"carte de contact sera servie comme fichier .vcf téléchargeable (fonctionne "
"sur tous les scanners)."

#: src/Admin/Menu.php:157 src/Block/Maker.php:168
msgid ""
"Content too large to encode as a QR (max 2953 bytes at EC L). Shorten the "
"content."
msgstr ""
"Contenu trop volumineux pour un QR (max 2953 octets en EC L). Raccourcissez "
"le contenu."

